# Rule 03 - Enterprise Event Governance v2
# Part 1 - Event Strategy

# Purpose

Events are first-class architectural citizens.

Events communicate business facts.

Events are not method calls.

Events are immutable.

Events enable

- Loose Coupling
- Scalability
- Eventual Consistency
- Workflow Automation
- AI Orchestration
- Plugin Extensibility
- CQRS
- Auditability

Every event must represent a meaningful business occurrence.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Event Philosophy

Business Activity

↓

Business Fact

↓

Domain Event

↓

Integration Event

↓

Consumers

↓

Business Action

Events describe

"What Happened"

Never

"What Should Happen"

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Event Driven Architecture

The platform is Event Driven.

Services collaborate through

REST

↓

Immediate Query

Kafka

↓

Business Facts

Workflow

↓

Long Running Coordination

Saga

↓

Distributed Consistency

Never use events as remote method calls.

